snippet.title: Story Based Project: Amber Fraser
snippet.description: Amber shares some real experiences of what being in the midst of multiple pandemics is like for her, as well as pathways through these moments. Our stories deserve to be told and heard, for what we do now determines our future and that of generations to come. Right now, we are all shaping history, and it is with duty that we shift the narrative of who, how, when, where, and why we fight for collective liberation and healing.
